1987;;The Pick-up Artist;;American;;James Toback;;Robert Downey, Jr., Molly Ringwald, Dennis Hopper;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Pick-up_Artist_(film);;Randy Jensen is a smart, independent tour guide who beats womanizer Jack Jericho at his own game. After a quick fling, her indifference only causes him to become smitten with her.<br><br>Randy is too busy for romance, trying to keep her alcoholic gambler father, Flash Jensen, out of harm's way. Jack's persistence soon pays off when he offers to help rescue Randy's dad from the mob.